{
  "texts": [
    "OPT-IML Bench (Iyer et al, 2022).",
    "The OPT-IML Bench dataset comprises 2K NLP task datasets spanning 93 task types.",
    "The creators integrate and filter eight large data repositories, including the CrossFit, UnifiedSKG (Xie et al, 2022), PromptSource (Bach et al, 2022), and others.",
    "OPT-IML Bench is utilized to investigate the impact of a series of decisions in instruction fine-tuning on the downstream task performance.",
    "PromptSource (Bach et al, 2022)."
  ]
}